quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  71,1,"Men nulii Nuuhu haa e yim…ìe makko …ìen, wonnde : \"Jertin yim…ìe maa …ìen, ado lette muusu…óe arde e ma…ì…ìe"
  71,2,"O maakani […ìe] : \"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, min ko mi jertinoowo on …ìanngu…óo"
  71,3,"wonnde yo on rewu Allah, hulon Mo, …óofto…óon lam"
  71,4,"O haforanay on junuubi mon …óin, O nenna on haa e lajal ta∆¥aangal. [Ko woni tun] lajal Allah ngal si hewtii, ngal nennetaake, si tawii hi…óon anndunoo"
  71,5,"O maaki : \"Joomi am, min mi noddirii yim…ìe am …ìen jemma e √±alorma"
  71,6,"kono noddaandu am ndun …ìeydaali …ìe, si wanaa dogugol"
  71,7,"Tuma kala kadi nde mi noddi …ìe fii no Hafaranaa …ìe, …ìe wa…óay kolli ma…ì…ìe …óin ka nder noppi ma…ì…ìe, …ìe buumora comci ma…ì…ìe …óin, …ìe deppitoo, …ìe townitora townitaadee"
  71,8,Refti mi noddirii …ìe e kene
  71,9,"Refti mi fe√±√±inani …ìe, mi gunndii …ìe gunndaadee"
  71,10,"Mi wi'i […ìe] : \"Insinanee Joomi mon, tawde O siforii wonnde Haforoow"
  71,11,O wurtira to…ìo ngon e mo'on rewnindiral
  71,12,"O …ìeydira on jawle e …ìi…ó…ìe, O wa…óana on gese, O wa…óana on can…ói"
  71,13,"E ko he…ìi on, on jortaaki manngural Allah ngal"
  71,14,Hara le O tagir on taa…ìe-taa…ìe
  71,15,E on yi'aali no Allah tagiri kammuulli jee…ói…ói tegondir…ói
  71,16,"O wa…ói lewru ndun jal…ìundu e majji, O wa…ói naange ngen pitilol"
  71,17,Ko Allah fu…óniri on ka leydi fu…ónugol
  71,18,"refti O ruttiray on e mayri, O yaltina on yaltinndee"
  71,19,Allah wa…óiranii on leydi ndin weertaandi
  71,20,fii yo on naatir e mayri laawi yaaju…ói
  71,21,"Nuuhu maaki : \"Joomi am, …ìee yeddii lam, …ìe jokkii on mo jawle mun e …ìi…ó…ìe …ìeydaali …óum si wanaa hayrugol"
  71,22,∆Åe fewji feere mawnde
  71,23,"…ìe wi'i: \"Wata on terto dey rewetee…ói mon …óin: wata on terto Wudda, e Suwaa'a, e Ya'uuqatha, e Nasr"
  71,24,"Ko pellet, …ìe majjinii ko …óuu…ói. [Joomi] wata A …ìeydir too√±u…ìe …ìen, si wanaa majjere"
  71,25,"Ko sagu goopi ma…ì…ìe …óin …ìe yooliranoo, …ìe naadaa Yiite, …ìe he…ìanaano ko'e ma…ì…ìe faabotoo…óo gaanin Allah"
  71,26,"Nuuhu maaki kadi : \"Joomi am, wata A accu e leydi ndin, hay keefeero dilloowo"
  71,27,"Ko pellet, si A accii …ìe, …ìe majjinay jeyaa…ìe Maa …ìen, …ìe jiidoytaako si wanaa bonnoo…ìe …óuu…óu…ìe geddi"
  71,28,"Joomi am, haforanam min e jibim…ìe lam …ìen, e …ìen gom…óim…ìe naatu…ìe ka suudu am, e gom…óim…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e gom…óim…ìe rew…ìe …ìen; wata A …ìeydir too√±u…ìe …ìen, si wanaa halakuyee"